1
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:07,500
Nishikata, have you ever had canned coffee?

2
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:12,000
Of course I have. I've had it lots of times.

3
00:00:13,500 --> 00:00:16,800
Oh really? Then what about black coffee?

4
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:21,500
Black? I can drink black coffee too... probably.

5
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:26,200
"Probably"? Have you really had it before?

6
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:31,500
I have! I can appreciate grown-up flavors!

7
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:36,000
Then let's go buy some. There's a vending machine.

8
00:00:37,500 --> 00:00:40,800
Huh... right now? I mean, sure, that's fine.

9
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:45,500
Here, a black coffee. Here you go.

10
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:50,300
Thanks. Okay, let's drink them together.

11
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:55,000
Ready, set...

12
00:00:56,500 --> 00:00:59,800
B-Bitter...! But, it's fine. I can drink it.

13
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:04,500
You don't have to force yourself. Your face looks terrible.

14
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:09,200
I'm not forcing anything! Something like this is nothing!

15
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:14,000
I actually like black coffee quite a bit.

16
00:01:15,500 --> 00:01:18,800
No way... You actually think it tastes good?

17
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:23,500
Yeah. Once you get used to it, it becomes delicious.

18
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:28,500
Coffee with sugar is definitely better, though.

19
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:33,200
Well, you don't have to force yourself to drink black, you know.

20
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:38,500
Damn, I feel like I lost to Takagi-san again.
